The claim originated from a self: described satirical publication called America's Last Line of Defense, indicating that it was not based on factual information.
The photo used in the meme is not of Ale: Cortez, as it can be found on a meme-generating website and was posted on Flickr in 2008 with a tag for Los Angeles. The woman in the photo is named Stephanie, not Ocasio-Cortez.
